{"tid":193181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★新招滅IT：巨大壓力，逼其自動消失！","createTime":"2017-04-09T06:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T06:42:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbdcbc8f70239ac7313c210cd77ca77dd538d402","tid":193181,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"前線人員訴苦稱<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就連負責維修空管系統的外判公司人員亦捱不住壓力，部份人寧願辭職轉工或進修</span>，民航處空管人員卻苦於自己屬專業職位，難以轉工，對上司的高壓管治或不合理要求，往往敢怒不敢言。他憶述，去年10月底新空管系統最後測試時，多部電腦死機發出警號，當時有同事拍下電腦故障畫面傳給傳媒，引起民航處高層震動，隨即瀰漫白色恐怖氣氛。管理層除嚴厲訓斥下屬、強調空管中心絕不容拍照外，據悉甚至檢查部份同事手機，意圖找出洩密者。至去年11月新空管系統全面啟用後，員工為新系統填寫問卷評價系統表現時，又被上司下令不准給予低分，必須唱好，令同事反感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170409/56540104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170409%2F56540104&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dcdfe346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170409%2F56540104&h=bb64277f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170409/56540104</a>"},{"pid":"986b36d4cb3076319aa128dbaa6a1e8249c174ba","tid":193181,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec8a2d40dd6eef7c640b00f6c446b96c91abb01","tid":193181,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4164c9ffc8600bc0e2ed98eaf5201c47526678e3","tid":193181,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T06:42:06.000